function case_label:
at D0 : contract: ensures \old(i) == i + 1;
at d0 : assert \at(i,Pre) + 1 == i;
at c1 : contract: ensures \old(i) + 1 == i;
at d1 : assert i == \at(i,D1);
at D1 : assert i + 1 == \at(i,D0);

function label:
at L0: contract: ensures import: i ≡ \old(i) + 1;
at L1: contract: ensures import: i ≡ \old(i) + 1;
